45
00:02:29,814 --> 00:02:32,206
Hearin' you loud and clear, boss

46
00:02:32,206 --> 00:02:35,017
Doer better still be out there

47
00:02:35,309 --> 00:02:37,948
Kind of job you hate the most to catch,

48
00:02:37,948 --> 00:02:40,970
but worth the most to close

49
00:03:16,808 --> 00:03:18,105
Miller

50
00:03:18,105 --> 00:03:20,283
Oh, crap

51
