You heard about that, huh?

63
00:03:53,042 --> 00:03:55,251
Fellow cop gets shot,
word gets out

64
00:03:55,251 --> 00:03:57,815
Well, anyway, uh,
I made my peace with that,

65
00:03:57,815 --> 00:04:01,641
it's just some scheduled stuff
I gotta look at

66
